sentences.english: They send out Nils Fingleton, the croc man.

sentences.english: The count turned round as he heard the entrance of Danglars into the room.
sentences.chinese: 伯爵聽到騰格拉爾進來的聲音就轉過身來。

sentences.english: Because we made time and space independently, was we in fact violating the time-out rule?

sentences.english: Of what packet are you speaking, Danglars?
sentences.chinese: 你說的是一包什麼東西，騰格拉爾？
